metadata.name: Mr . Earrr
metadata.description:
I decided to move to Rome, but Mr Ear asked me to take him to see Florence which was born there, do you know why ???
because he has not yet seen Florence, he alone has heard from me and others that Florence is a wonderful city of the 15th century
but I decided to take him on a tour of Florence before leaving for Rome.
today we went to see the old bridge
the ponte vecchio is a famous bridge in Florence that spans the Arno river in Florence, approximately 150 meters.
Mr Ear took a wonderful picture on the bridge with Arno

if you want to see him where he goes next time in Florence follow him.
